title: Bobby Going To The Brain Doctor + Lunchbox Tries For Free Donuts + Throwback Thursday With Clay Walker!
itunes:title: Bobby Going To The Brain Doctor + Lunchbox Tries For Free Donuts + Throwback Thursday With Clay Walker!
description:
Bobby's going to the brain doctor today because he's having trouble remembering things. Lunchbox goes to Krispy Kreme to see if the free dozen donuts for the Class Of 2020 students was really a thing! Plus, it's Throwback Thursday and we're celebrating with new music from Clay Walker!
